WeightWatcher is a program that combines weight-maps, flag-maps and
polygon data in order to produce control maps which can directly be
used in astronomical image-processing packages like Swarp or
SExtractor.

This file describes shortly the SYNTAX of WeightWatcher.
See INSTALL for instructions about install.
For more information, please refer to the documentation
(see http://terapix.iap.fr/soft/weightwatcher/ )

The general SYNTAX or WeightWatcher is:

% ww [-c <configuration_file>] [-<keyword> <value>]

Please report any bug or strange behaviour on the Forum
http://terapix.iap.fr/forum/forumdisplay.php?fid=18.

